## 4. Features

### Core Feature Set
1. **Human-like turn-by-turn guidance** — AI-generated, landmark-based, conversational instructions layered on Google Maps routing data.
2. **Voice narration (TTS)** — Natural-sounding spoken guidance, adjustable tone/pace/style.
3. **Live map view** — Standard interactive map (Google Maps SDK) with route overlay.
4. **Landmark & context awareness** — References visible, recognizable points (buildings, shops, signals) instead of only distances.
5. **Trip history & saved places** — Home, work, favorites; past trips log.
6. **Real-time traffic-aware rerouting** — Adjusts route and narration when conditions change.
7. **Multi-modal support** — Driving, walking, (future: cycling/transit).
8. **Authentication & profile sync** — Firebase-based sign-in, cross-device sync.
9. **Push notifications** — Trip start reminders, arrival notices, traffic alerts.
10. **Personalization** — Learns user's preferred phrasing/verbosity over time (future phase).

