## 7. User Stories

### Authentication & Onboarding
- As a **new user**, I want to sign up with Google or email via Firebase, so I can quickly start using the app.
- As a **returning user**, I want my trip history and saved places synced across devices, so I don't lose my data.

### Core Navigation
- As a **driver**, I want to enter a destination and get a route, so I can start navigating.
- As a **driver**, I want instructions phrased naturally (e.g., "turn right after the bakery") instead of only distances, so I can navigate more intuitively.
- As a **driver**, I want spoken narration of directions, so I don't need to look at my phone while driving.
- As a **driver in an unfamiliar area**, I want landmark-based cues, so I feel more confident I'm on the right track.

### Trip Management
- As a **user**, I want to see my past trips, so I can quickly re-navigate to frequent destinations.
- As a **user**, I want to save "Home" and "Work," so I can start navigation with one tap.

### Reliability
- As a **user**, if the AI-generated instruction service fails, I want to fall back to standard Google Maps-style instructions, so I'm never left without guidance.
- As a **user**, I want to receive a notification when I'm close to my destination, so I can prepare to park/exit.

### Accessibility
- As a **visually impaired user**, I want detailed, descriptive audio cues, so I can navigate without relying on the screen.

