## 8. Success Metrics

### Product/Engagement Metrics
- **Daily/Monthly Active Users (DAU/MAU)**
- **Trip completion rate** (routes started vs. successfully completed without abandonment)
- **Retention** (Day 1 / Day 7 / Day 30 retention)
- **Session frequency** — average navigation sessions per active user per week

### Quality Metrics (core differentiator)
- **Instruction clarity rating** — post-trip user rating ("Were the directions easy to follow?")
- **Missed-turn rate** — frequency of user deviating from route at a guided turn (proxy for instruction clarity)
- **A/B preference score** — % of users preferring AI Navigation's phrasing vs. standard robotic instructions in comparative testing
- **Voice narration comprehension** — % of instructions requiring the user to glance at the screen despite audio guidance

### Technical Metrics
- **API latency** — time from route request to first instruction rendered (target: < 2s)
- **Uptime/availability** of FastAPI backend and dependency services
- **Fallback-trigger rate** — how often the system falls back to raw Google Maps instructions due to AI-layer failure

### Business Metrics (later stages)
- **Conversion to paid tier** (if freemium model introduced)
- **B2B licensing interest/signed pilots** (Phase 5+)

