| **Month 5** | Closed beta (driving mode only) with real users, collect instruction-quality feedback |
| **Month 6** | Public MVP launch (driving mode, iOS + Android) |
| **Month 7–8** | Phase 2: walking/cycling modes, saved places, trip history UI |
| **Month 9–10** | Phase 3: real-time traffic-aware rerouting, offline caching |
| **Month 11–12** | Phase 4: personalization engine, multi-language support |
| **Year 2** | Phase 5–6: public API/SDK, B2B partnerships, CarPlay/Android Auto, wearables |

